org.javaavc.ffmpeg.avformat

Interface LibavformatLibrary.AVDurationEstimationMethod

  • Enclosing interface:
    LibavformatLibrary

    public static interface LibavformatLibrary.AVDurationEstimationMethod
    The duration of a video can be estimated through various ways, and this enum can be used
    to know how the duration was estimated.
    enum values
